                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8535" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2145</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1066 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">破局与重塑：米奥会展疫情下的组织适应与数字化转型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Breaking and reshaping: Organizational adaptation and digital transformation of Meorient under the epidemic</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">范志刚，陈显骅</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杭州师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江米奥兰特商务会展股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织韧性；数字化；一带一路；跨国经营</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Organizational Resilience；Digitalization；The Belt And Road；Multinational Op-erations</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">米奥会展是国内第一家在创业板上市的主营展览主办业务的民营公司，成立初期主要聚焦代理展业务，随着公司稳步成长，其战略视线逐渐转向自主举办的海外展览，特别是在“一带一路”沿线市场的深入布局，凭借其深厚的行业积淀与广泛的资源网络，逐步确立了行业领头羊的地位。然而，公司在资本市场成功登陆不久即遭遇新冠疫情的严峻挑战，传统展览业务遭受重创。在入不敷出的严峻形势下，米奥会展凭借对宏观经济形势的分析与对会展行业的理解顺势抓住政策机遇；进而有的放矢、因时制宜地实施组织变革，并在危机情形下激发组织活力；最终乘势而上孕育出满足市场需求的数字化产品，并在危机环境发生变化时快速迭代产品以适应新环境；“三维联动”转型成功帮助米奥会展度过危机并实现反弹。本案例期望激发学生对于企业管理复杂性的深刻洞察，以及在不确定性中寻求发展机遇的策略思维。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Meorient Exhibition is the first private company listed on the GEM in China that is mainly engaged in exhibition hosting business. At the beginning of its establishment, Meorient Exhibition mainly focused on exhibition agent business. With the steady growth of the company, its strategic focus gradually turned to overseas exhibitions held independently, especially the in-depth layout of markets along the &quot;Belt and Road&quot;. Gradually established the industry leader position. However, shortly after the company&#39;s successful landing in the capital market, it encountered severe challenges from the new coronavirus epidemic, and the traditional exhibition business suffered heavy losses. In the severe situation of making ends meet, Meorient Exhibition seized the policy opportunity with its analysis of macroeconomic situation and understanding of the exhibition industry. Then implement organizational reform according to the time and target, and stimulate the vitality of the organization under the crisis situation. Finally, take advantage of the trend to breed digital products that meet the market de-mand, and quickly iterate products to adapt to the new environment when the crisis environment changes. The &quot;three-dimensional linkage&quot; transformation successfully helped Meorient Exhibition to overcome the crisis and achieve a rebound. This case study aims to stimulate students&#39; insight into the complexity of business management and strategic thinking in seeking growth opportunities amid uncertainty.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《组织行为学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织韧性的特征、作用及形成路径；数字化转型的概念及数字化转型对组织韧性构建的影响</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
